 4\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>&#x110;&#x1EC3; t&#xEC;m min c&#x1EE7;a c&#xE1;c ph&#x1EA7;n t&#x1EED; trong m&#x1EA3;ng</p>\n<p>Th&#x1EF1;c hi&#x1EC7;n v&#xF2;ng for ch&#x1EA1;y t&#x1EEB; 1 t&#x1EDB;i gi&#xE1; tr&#x1ECB; n.</p>\n<p>Ki&#x1EC3;m tra n&#x1EBF;u g&#x1EB7;p s&#x1ED1; nh&#x1ECF; h&#x1A1;n th&#xEC; g&#xE1;n l&#x1EA1;i</p>\n<pre><code>int sonhonhat = ds[0];\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        if (ds[i]&lt;sonhonhat)\n        {\n            sonhonhat = ds[i];\n        }\n    }</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"1.5      TH&#x1EF0;C H&#xC0;NH B&#x1AF;&#x1EDA;C 5\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>In k&#x1EBF;t qu&#x1EA3;</p>\n<pre><code>//In ra danh sach\n    printf(&quot;Danh sach da nhap la:&quot;);\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        printf(&quot;ds[%d]=%d\\n&quot;,i,ds[i]);\n    }\n    printf(&quot;Gia tri nho nhat [%d] \\n&quot;, sonhonhat);\n</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"*** II. Chuy&#x1EC3;n th&#xE0;nh h&#xE0;m\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>II.1 Khu&#xF4;n m&#x1EAB;u h&#xE0;m</p>\n<p>Khai b&#xE1;o 1 h&#xE0;m c&#xF3; khu&#xF4;n m&#x1EAB;u sau: Trong &#x111;&#xF3;, <code>timMax</code> l&#xE0; t&#xEA;n h&#xE0;m; tham s&#x1ED1; truy&#x1EC1;n v&#xE0;o l&#xE0; n s&#x1ED1; l&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;ng ph&#x1EA7;n t&#x1EED; trong m&#x1EA3;ng v&#xE0; danh s&#xE1;ch ds g&#x1ED3;m n ph&#x1EA7;n t&#x1EED;; </p>\n<p>K&#x1EBF;t qu&#x1EA3; tr&#x1EA3; ra gi&#xE1; tr&#x1ECB; nho nh&#x1EA5;t c&#x1EE7;a m&#x1EA3;ng</p>\n<pre><code>int timMin(int ds[], int n);</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"II.2 Code c&#x1EE7;a h&#xE0;m\" duration=\"0\">\n        <pre><code>int timMin(int ds[], int n)\n{\n    int sonhonhat = ds[0];\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        if (ds[i]&lt;sonhonhat)\n        {\n            sonhonhat = ds[i];\n        }\n    }\n    return sonhonhat;\n}</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"II.3 Code m&#x1EDB;i c&#x1EE7;a h&#xE0;m Main\" duration=\"0\">\n        <pre><code>int main()\n{\n    int ds[10];\n    int n;\n    int sonhonhat=9999999;\n    //Hien thong bao moi nguoi dung nhap\n    printf(&quot;Nhap so luong phan tu:&quot;);\n    //Nhap vao tu ban phim\n    scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;n);\n    //In n ra\n    printf(&quot;n=%d\\n&quot;,n);\n    //Nhap cac phan tu trong mang\n    for (int i = 0; i&lt;n; i++)\n    {\n        //In ra loi huong dan nhap phan tu thu may\n        printf(&quot;Nhap phan tu thu [%d]:&quot;,i+1);\n        scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;ds[i]);\n    }\n    printf(&quot;Min trong mang:\\n&quot;);\n\n    //goi ham\n    sonhonhat = timMin(ds,n);\n    //In ra danh sach\n    printf(&quot;Danh sach da nhap la:&quot;);\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        printf(&quot;ds[%d]=%d\\n&quot;,i,ds[i]);\n    }\n    printf(&quot;Gia tri nho nhat %d \\n&quot;, sonhonhat);\n    getch();\n}\nint timMin(int ds[], int n)\n{\n    int sonhonhat = ds[0];\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        if (ds[i]&lt;sonhonhat)\n        {\n            sonhonhat = ds[i];\n        }\n    }\n    return sonhonhat;\n}</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"II.4 Code to&#xE0;n b&#x1ED9; c&#x1EE7;a ch&#x1B0;&#x1A1;ng tr&#xEC;nh l&#xE0;\" duration=\"0\">\n        <pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;\n#include &lt;conio.h&gt;\nint timMin(int ds[], int n);\nint main()\n{\n    int ds[10];\n    int n;\n    int sonhonhat=9999999;\n    //Hien thong bao moi nguoi dung nhap\n    printf(&quot;Nhap so luong phan tu:&quot;);\n    //Nhap vao tu ban phim\n    scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;n);\n    //In n ra\n    printf(&quot;n=%d\\n&quot;,n);\n    //Nhap cac phan tu trong mang\n    for (int i = 0; i&lt;n; i++)\n    {\n        //In ra loi huong dan nhap phan tu thu may\n        printf(&quot;Nhap phan tu thu [%d]:&quot;,i+1);\n        scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;ds[i]);\n    }\n    printf(&quot;Min trong mang:\\n&quot;);\n\n    //goi ham\n    sonhonhat = timMin(ds,n);\n    //In ra danh sach\n    printf(&quot;Danh sach da nhap la:&quot;);\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        printf(&quot;ds[%d]=%d\\n&quot;,i,ds[i]);\n    }\n    printf(&quot;Gia tri nho nhat %d \\n&quot;, sonhonhat);\n    getch();\n}\nint timMin(int ds[], int n)\n{\n    int sonhonhat = ds[0];\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        if (ds[i]&lt;sonhonhat)\n        {\n            sonhonhat = ds[i];\n        }\n    }\n    return sonhonhat;\n}</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://laptrinhcodeblock.blogspot.com/p/bai-tap-thuc-hanh-lap-trinh-c.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xem th&#xEA;m c&#xE1;c b&#xE0;i vi&#x1EBF;t th&#x1EF1;c h&#xE0;nh t&#x1EA1;i &#x111;&#xE2;y</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://laptrinhcodeblock.blogspot.com/2019/03/thuc-hanh-goi-ham-tim-gia-tri-nho-nhat.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://laptrinhcodeblock.blogspot.com/2019/03/thuc-hanh-goi-ham-tim-gia-tri-nho-nhat.html</a></p>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n  </google-codelab>\n\n  <script src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/codelab-elements/native-shim.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/codelab-elements/custom-elements.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/codelab-elements/prettify.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/codelab-elements/codelab-elements.js\"></script>\n\n\n\n','ejjddjdj','',6,81,'2019-10-18 08:57:53','2019-10-18 08:57:53'),
	(37,'10OxALgLq5UgFUCTSt7HVr_I6AT34kkEXa9itYO_h4Wo','Chưa được đặt tiêu đề','\n<!doctype html>\n\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, minimum-scale=1.0, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes\">\n  <meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#4F7DC9\">\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title></title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Code+Pro:400|Roboto:400,300,400italic,500,700|Roboto+Mono\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/codelab-elements/codelab-elements.css\">\n  <style>\n    .success {\n      color: #1e8e3e;\n    }\n    .error {\n      color: red;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <google-codelab-analytics gaid=\"UA-49880327-14\"></google-codelab-analytics>\n  <google-codelab codelab-gaid=\"\"\n                  id=\"\"\n                  title=\"\"\n                  environment=\"web\"\n                  feedback-link=\"\">\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"1.1     THỰC HÀNH BƯỚC 1\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>Mở Code Blocks → New File → Empty file --&gt; Lưu file HamTimMinCuaMang có đuôi .cpp</p>\n<p class=\"image-container\"><img style=\"width: 700.80px\" src=\"img/d973026e921a44a8.png\"></p>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"1.2      THỰC HÀNH BƯỚC 2\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>Khai báo sử dụng các thư viện</p>\n<pre><code>#include &lt;conio.h&gt;\n#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"1.3      THỰC HÀNH BƯỚC 3\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>Khai báo biến và mảng sử dụng trong chương trình</p>\n<pre><code>int ds[10];\n    int n;\n    int sonhonhat=9999999;\n    //Hien thong bao moi nguoi dung nhap\n    printf(&#34;Nhap so luong phan tu:&#34;);\n    //Nhap vao tu ban phim\n    scanf(&#34;%d&#34;,&amp;n);\n    //In n ra\n    printf(&#34;n=%d\\n&#34;,n);\n    //Nhap cac phan tu trong mang\n    for (int i = 0; i&lt;n; i++)\n    {\n        //In ra loi huong dan nhap phan tu thu may\n        printf(&#34;Nhap phan tu thu [%d]:&#34;,i+1);\n        scanf(&#34;%d&#34;,&amp;ds[i]);\n    }\n\n</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"1.4      THỰC HÀNH BƯỚC 4\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>Để tìm min của các phần tử trong mảng</p>\n<p>Thực hiện vòng for chạy từ 1 tới giá trị n.</p>\n<p>Kiểm tra nếu gặp số nhỏ hơn thì gán lại</p>\n<pre><code>int sonhonhat = ds[0];\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        if (ds[i]&lt;sonhonhat)\n        {\n            sonhonhat = ds[i];\n        }\n    }</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"1.5      THỰC HÀNH BƯỚC 5\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>In kết quả</p>\n<pre><code>//In ra danh sach\n    printf(&#34;Danh sach da nhap la:&#34;);\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        printf(&#34;ds[%d]=%d\\n&#34;,i,ds[i]);\n    }\n    printf(&#34;Gia tri nho nhat [%d] \\n&#34;, sonhonhat);\n</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"*** II. Chuyển thành hàm\" duration=\"0\">\n        <p>II.1 Khuôn mẫu hàm</p>\n<p>Khai báo 1 hàm có khuôn mẫu sau: Trong đó, <code>timMax</code> là tên hàm; tham số truyền vào là n số lượng phần tử trong mảng và danh sách ds gồm n phần tử; </p>\n<p>Kết quả trả ra giá trị nho nhất của mảng</p>\n<pre><code>int timMin(int ds[], int n);</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"II.2 Code của hàm\" duration=\"0\">\n        <pre><code>int timMin(int ds[], int n)\n{\n    int sonhonhat = ds[0];\n    for (int i = 0;i&lt;n;i++)\n    {\n        if (ds[i]&lt;sonhonhat)\n        {\n            sonhonhat = ds[i];\n        }\n    }\n    return sonhonhat;\n}</code></pre>\n\n\n      </google-codelab-step>\n    \n      <google-codelab-step label=\"II.3 Code mới của hàm Main\